data.description: This cute home situated in a quiet cul-de-sac is loaded with potential! A wonderful starter home...just add "love"...or a great investment property. The front lawn is very large and perfect for any yard games. The back yard offers tons of privacy and plenty of garden space as well as a large deck and storage building. Inside you'll find 3 spacious bedrooms and two full baths. The kitchen is large enough for a 6 top table or add an island. The formal dining room is situated adjacent to the kitchen and offers natural light from the window looking onto the deck. The living room is large enough for a sectional and other seating. The den is perfect for relaxing with a book or could be used as a home office. There's tons of storage space available in this cute rancher! Don't wait to schedule your showing today!
